<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/490817-i-read-something-pretty-gruesome-about">I read something pretty gruesome about this book. It involved the protagonist, his trade as a bow-maker, and his nephew. That&#39;s all I&#39;ll say.

There was no context given about this scene but what I read definitely made me sick. Does context make this scene any easier to handle?</a>
</div>
