    <a title="Ee Cheng Ooi" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/19134445-ee-cheng-ooi"><img alt="Ee Cheng Ooi" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

