        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1887520920" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer986144706193608407">People have rated this book poorly, with the claim that it violates the rule of heroic fantasy - that the hero has to be heroic. I don&apos;t hold to this in the slightest, and thus thoroughly enjoyed the novel.</span>
  <span id="freeText986144706193608407" style="display:none">People have rated this book poorly, with the claim that it violates the rule of heroic fantasy - that the hero has to be heroic. I don't hold to this in the slightest, and thus thoroughly enjoyed the novel.</span>
  <a data-text-id="986144706193608407" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
