      <span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_review_1245331396'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it gr-button gr-button--small" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F427066.The_Belly_of_the_Bow">Like</a></span>
