      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/240708.K_J_Parker">About K.J. Parker</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
