<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/240708.K_J_Parker"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1607271294p3/240708.jpg);'></div>
